---
title: Beef Koftas & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Cucumber Raita
description: These koftas are handy parcels of flavour, with tender mince, mild spices and a smattering of almonds to add extra texture.
Paired with a veggie-packed couscous and tangy yoghurt, this is a Middle Eastern feast to remember.
